title: Treasury Services Act 2020 (No. 6 of 2020) shall come into operation.
heading: 1. This Order may be cited as the National Oil Reserves Agency
text_raw:
1. This Order may be cited as the National Oil Reserves Agency 
(Amendment) and Provision of Central Treasury Services Act 2020 
(Commencement) Order 2020.

title: Treasury Services Act 2020 (No. 6 of 2020) shall come into operation.
heading: 2. The 1st day of August 2020 is appointed as the day on which the
text_raw:
2. The 1st day of August 2020 is appointed as the day on which the 
National Oil Reserves Agency (Amendment) and Provision of Central 
Treasury Services Act 2020 (No. 6 of 2020) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

30 July 2020. 

EAMON RYAN 

Minister for Communications, Climate Action 

and Environment. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 4th August, 2020.
